com.dsi.ant.message

Class MessageId

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.dsi.ant.message.MessageId

  • public final class MessageId
extends java.lang.Object
    Defines the message IDs used in the ANT protocol to identify the contents and format of an AntMessageFromAnt. Used for setting and decoding AntMessageFromAnt.getMessageId().
    Since:
    4.0
